description.narrative: (Somalia): .The Strengthening Somali Governance (SSG) activity will support the development of more effective and accountable government institutions in Somalia at the national level, Puntland State, and Somaliland. This activity will improve the legislative, oversight, and representational functions of Somalia's deliberative bodies, improve the ability of targeted government institutions to carry out their essential functions, and increase civil society and media engagement in political processes. SSG will complement USAID's stabilization efforts by improving the government's capacity to respond to citizen needs and feedback, and to deliver essential government services... ..
